---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Membership Plans – Bliss Dermacare" description="Join a Bliss Dermacare membership and enjoy monthly facials, lash & body services, and exclusive discounts. Three tiers starting at $89/month. Cancel anytime.">

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-50 via-primary-50 to-amber-50 border-b border-primary-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-5">
        <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"/></svg>
        Member Plans
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-5">Glow Every Month.<br class="hidden sm:block" /> Save Every Visit.</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">Stop booking one-off appointments. Become a member and lock in monthly treatments at a fraction of the cost — with perks that make every visit feel like a luxury.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-sm text-neutral-600">
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>No contracts or commitments</span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Cancel anytime</span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>VIP plan includes credit rollover</span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Pause up to 60 days/year</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Value Snapshot -->
  <section class="py-8 bg-neutral-900 border-b border-neutral-800">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif text-white">$10–$132</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 mt-1 uppercase tracking-wide">Saved monthly vs. pay-as-you-go</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif text-primary-400">3 Tiers</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 mt-1 uppercase tracking-wide">For every skincare goal</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif text-white">Priority</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 mt-1 uppercase tracking-wide">Booking for all members</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif text-amber-400">Exclusive</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 mt-1 uppercase tracking-wide">Member-only perks & upgrades</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Membership Plans -->
  <section id="plans" class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">

      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-3">Choose Your Plan</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 max-w-xl mx-auto">Every plan includes priority booking and a member discount. Upgrade or downgrade anytime.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 items-stretch">

        <!-- TIER 1: The Glow Ritual -->
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl border-2 border-neutral-200 hover:border-primary-300 hover:shadow-xl transition-all bg-white flex flex-col overflow-hidden group">
          <div class="p-7 flex-1">
            <div class="mb-5">
              <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary-500 mb-2">Tier 1</p>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-1">The Glow Ritual</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">For the consistent skincare client who wants glowing skin year-round.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-6">
              <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900">$89</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-neutral-400">/month</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-emerald-700 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">Save up to $10/mo</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Included Services -->
            <div class="mb-6">
              <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-400 mb-3">What's Included Monthly</p>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-primary-50 rounded-xl border border-primary-100">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900">1 Facial Credit</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mt-0.5">Choose from: Signature Radiance ($99), Pineapple Enzyme ($88), Skin Recovery ($92), Pumpkin Enzyme ($85), or Teen Facial ($64)</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Perks -->
            <div class="space-y-2.5">
              <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-400 mb-2">Member Perks</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span><strong class="text-neutral-800">10% off</strong> all additional services booked</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span>Priority scheduling — book before non-members</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span>Cancel or pause anytime</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Retail vs Member Comparison -->
          <div class="mx-7 mb-6 p-3 bg-neutral-50 rounded-xl border border-neutral-100 text-xs">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-1">
              <span class="text-neutral-500">Retail price (monthly)</span>
              <span class="text-neutral-400 line-through">$99</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold">
              <span class="text-neutral-700">Member price</span>
              <span class="text-primary-600">$89/mo</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="px-7 pb-7">
            <button
              data-plan="glow-ritual"
              data-plan-name="The Glow Ritual"
              data-plan-price="89"
              onclick="openMembershipSignup(this)"
              class="w-full py-3.5 rounded-xl border-2 border-primary-600 text-primary-600 font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-primary-600 hover:text-white transition-all">
              Start Glow Ritual — $89/mo
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- TIER 2: The Radiance Plan — MOST POPULAR -->
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl border-2 border-primary-500 hover:border-primary-600 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all bg-white flex flex-col overflow-hidden group shadow-xl">
          <!-- Popular badge -->
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 bg-primary-600 text-white text-xs font-bold text-center py-2 tracking-[0.15em] uppercase">
            ✦ Most Popular
          </div>
          <div class="p-7 pt-11 flex-1">
            <div class="mb-5">
              <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary-500 mb-2">Tier 2</p>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-1">The Radiance Plan</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Two services per month — a premium facial plus your choice of lash, brow, or body treatment.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-6">
              <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900">$159</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-neutral-400">/month</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-emerald-700 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">Save up to $56/mo</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Included Services -->
            <div class="mb-6">
              <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-400 mb-3">What's Included Monthly</p>
              <div class="space-y-2.5">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-primary-50 rounded-xl border border-primary-100">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900">1 Premium Facial Credit <span class="text-xs text-neutral-400 font-normal">(up to $128 value)</span></p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mt-0.5">Diamond Glow, Brightening Peel, Dermaplane Glow, Chlorophyll Skin Tightening, Smooth Canvas, High Frequency + all Tier 1 facials</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-rose-50 rounded-xl border border-rose-100">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-rose-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900">1 Lash, Brow, or Body Credit <span class="text-xs text-neutral-400 font-normal">(up to $87 value)</span></p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mt-0.5">Lash Lift & Brow Lamination ($79), Body & Face Waxing ($65), Brazilian Wax ($87), or Custom Spray Tan ($65)</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Perks -->
            <div class="space-y-2.5">
              <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-400 mb-2">Member Perks</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span><strong class="text-neutral-800">15% off</strong> all additional services booked</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span>Priority scheduling — skip the waitlist</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span>Free skin consultation included</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span>Cancel or pause anytime</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Retail vs Member Comparison -->
          <div class="mx-7 mb-6 p-3 bg-neutral-50 rounded-xl border border-neutral-100 text-xs">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-1">
              <span class="text-neutral-500">Retail value (monthly)</span>
              <span class="text-neutral-400 line-through">$128 + $87 = $215</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold">
              <span class="text-neutral-700">Member price</span>
              <span class="text-primary-600">$159/mo</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="px-7 pb-7">
            <button
              data-plan="radiance-plan"
              data-plan-name="The Radiance Plan"
              data-plan-price="159"
              onclick="openMembershipSignup(this)"
              class="w-full py-3.5 rounded-xl bg-primary-600 text-white font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-primary-700 transition-all shadow-md hover:shadow-lg">
              Start Radiance Plan — $159/mo
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- TIER 3: The VIP Luxe -->
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl border-2 border-neutral-200 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow-xl transition-all bg-white flex flex-col overflow-hidden group">
          <div class="p-7 flex-1">
            <div class="mb-5">
              <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-amber-500 mb-2">Tier 3 — VIP</p>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-1">The Bliss VIP</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Three services every month plus quarterly bonuses — the ultimate self-care routine at maximum savings.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-6">
              <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900">$249</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-neutral-400">/month</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-emerald-700 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">Save up to $132/mo</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Included Services -->
            <div class="mb-6">
              <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-400 mb-3">What's Included Monthly</p>
              <div class="space-y-2.5">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-primary-50 rounded-xl border border-primary-100">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900">1 Premium Facial Credit <span class="text-xs text-neutral-400 font-normal">(any facial up to $128)</span></p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mt-0.5">All facials from Tier 1 & 2</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-amber-50 rounded-xl border border-amber-100">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900">1 Lash Service Credit <span class="text-xs text-neutral-400 font-normal">(up to $159 value)</span></p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mt-0.5">Full Lash Extensions ($159), Lash Fill ($43), or Lash Lift & Brow Lamination ($79)</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-rose-50 rounded-xl border border-rose-100">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-rose-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900">1 Body Treatment Credit <span class="text-xs text-neutral-400 font-normal">(up to $87 value)</span></p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mt-0.5">Body & Face Waxing ($65), Brazilian Wax ($87), or Custom Spray Tan ($65)</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Perks -->
            <div class="space-y-2.5">
              <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-400 mb-2">VIP Member Perks</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span><strong class="text-neutral-800">20% off</strong> all additional services & packages</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span>VIP first-access booking window</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span><strong class="text-neutral-800">Quarterly bonus</strong>: 1 complimentary seasonal package upgrade (up to $185 value)</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span>Free personalized skincare plan every 6 months</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span>Unused credits roll over <strong class="text-neutral-800">30 days</strong></span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span>Cancel or pause anytime</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Retail vs Member Comparison -->
          <div class="mx-7 mb-6 p-3 bg-neutral-50 rounded-xl border border-neutral-100 text-xs">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-1">
              <span class="text-neutral-500">Retail value (monthly)</span>
              <span class="text-neutral-400 line-through">$128 + $159 + $87 = $374+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold">
              <span class="text-neutral-700">Member price</span>
              <span class="text-amber-600">$249/mo</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="px-7 pb-7">
            <button
              data-plan="vip-luxe"
              data-plan-name="The Bliss VIP"
              data-plan-price="249"
              onclick="openMembershipSignup(this)"
              class="w-full py-3.5 rounded-xl border-2 border-amber-500 text-amber-700 font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-amber-500 hover:text-white transition-all">
              Join VIP Luxe — $249/mo
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div><!-- /grid -->

      <!-- Fine Print -->
      <p class="text-center text-xs text-neutral-400 mt-6">All memberships are billed monthly via secure Stripe. Cancel or pause through the confirmation email link. Member credits cannot be transferred. Discounts do not stack with other promotions. Subject to availability.</p>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Understanding Credits — Deep Explainer -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-[#faf9f7] border-y border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">

      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary-600 mb-3">No Confusion, Ever</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-3">How Credits Work — Explained Simply</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 max-w-xl mx-auto">Credits are the heart of your membership. Here's exactly what they are, how to use them, and what happens each month.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- What is a credit -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 p-7">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900">What exactly is a "credit"?</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">A credit is your <strong class="text-neutral-800">pre-paid entitlement to one full service</strong> — not a partial discount, not a coupon. When your plan renews each month, your credits unlock automatically and cover the <em>complete cost</em> of any eligible service within your tier.</p>
          <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-primary-100 text-sm">
            <p class="font-semibold text-primary-800 mb-1">Example:</p>
            <p class="text-primary-700">You're on the Radiance Plan ($159/mo). Your plan unlocks <strong>1 facial credit + 1 lash/brow/body credit</strong> each billing cycle. You book a Diamond Glow Facial ($119) and a Lash Lift & Brow Lamination ($79). Total retail value: <strong>$198</strong>. You pay: <strong>$0 at the appointment</strong> — it's already covered by your membership.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 p-7">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900">How to use your credits</h3>
          </div>
          <ol class="space-y-3 text-sm text-neutral-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-600 text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">1</span>
