          <div class="faq-a hidden px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-neutral-600 border-t border-neutral-100 pt-4 space-y-3">
            <p>Not quite. A credit is your pre-paid entitlement to <strong class="text-neutral-800">one complete service</strong> within your plan's eligible category. It's not a dollar amount or a gift card — it's a service slot that's already been paid for as part of your monthly fee.</p>
            <p>When you book and mention your membership, we match your appointment against your available credits and mark that credit as used for the cycle. You won't be separately charged for covered services — they're included in your membership price.</p>
            <p>Think of it like a gym membership: you pay monthly and that entitles you to use the gym. With Bliss memberships, each month's payment entitles you to the specific services in your plan.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-q w-full flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 text-left hover:bg-neutral-50 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900">How do I actually redeem my credits when booking?</span>
            <svg class="faq-icon w-4 h-4 text-neutral-400 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a hidden px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-neutral-600 border-t border-neutral-100 pt-4 space-y-3">
            <p>It's simple — just book your appointment as normal (online or by calling/texting) and mention your membership plan in the Notes field or when you speak with us. For example: <em>"I'm on the Radiance Plan — I'd like to use my facial credit for the Diamond Glow Facial."</em></p>
            <p>We'll verify your active membership, apply your credit to the service, and confirm your booking with priority status. If you're booking online via Stripe, you'll be charged $0 for the covered service — or if we process it manually, we'll simply not charge you for that service.</p>
            <p>You can also reach out at <a href="tel:+16093660857" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">(609) 366-0857</a> and we'll handle everything for you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-q w-full flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 text-left hover:bg-neutral-50 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900">What happens if I don't use my credit in a given month?</span>
            <svg class="faq-icon w-4 h-4 text-neutral-400 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a hidden px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-neutral-600 border-t border-neutral-100 pt-4 space-y-3">
            <p>For <strong class="text-neutral-800">Glow Ritual and Radiance Plan</strong>, credits are <strong class="text-neutral-800">use-it-or-lose-it</strong> — they expire at the end of the billing cycle they were issued in. If you're billed on June 1, your credits must be used before July 1.</p>
            <p><strong class="text-neutral-800">Bliss VIP members</strong> enjoy an exclusive 30-day rollover: if you don't use a credit in the current cycle, it carries over and remains valid for 30 additional days into the next cycle.</p>
            <p>If you know you'll be unavailable for an extended period, you can <strong class="text-neutral-800">pause your membership for up to 60 days per year</strong> regardless of plan. Just reach out before your next billing date and we'll pause the renewal so you don't lose money on unused months.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-q w-full flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 text-left hover:bg-neutral-50 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900">Can I use two credits in the same appointment?</span>
            <svg class="faq-icon w-4 h-4 text-neutral-400 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a hidden px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-neutral-600 border-t border-neutral-100 pt-4 space-y-3">
            <p>Yes — on plans that include multiple credits (Radiance Plan and Bliss VIP), you can use all of your credits in a single visit or spread them across separate appointments throughout the month. It's entirely up to you.</p>
            <p>For example, a Radiance Plan member could book a 2-service session: a Diamond Glow Facial (facial credit) and a Brazilian Wax (body credit) back to back in one visit. Both credits would be applied.</p>
            <p>Just note that multi-service visits are subject to scheduling availability, and each session has a max duration. We'll work with you to find a time that fits.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-q w-full flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 text-left hover:bg-neutral-50 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900">How does the member discount work on extra services?</span>
            <svg class="faq-icon w-4 h-4 text-neutral-400 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a hidden px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-neutral-600 border-t border-neutral-100 pt-4 space-y-3">
            <p>Your member discount (10% for Glow Ritual, 15% for Radiance, 20% for VIP) applies to any service you book <strong class="text-neutral-800">beyond your included credits</strong> in the same billing cycle.</p>
            <p>The discount does <em>not</em> apply to services already covered by your credits — those are already priced far below retail. But for anything extra you want to add, you'll automatically receive your tier's discount when we confirm the booking.</p>
            <p>The discount also applies to seasonal packages, advanced treatments (Scalp Therapy, PRP), and spray tans — so the more you visit, the more you save.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-q w-full flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 text-left hover:bg-neutral-50 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900">Can I cancel my membership?</span>
            <svg class="faq-icon w-4 h-4 text-neutral-400 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a hidden px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-neutral-600 border-t border-neutral-100 pt-4 space-y-3">
            <p>Yes — cancel anytime with no penalty or cancellation fee. Simply email, text, or call us before your next billing date and we'll cancel your renewal immediately.</p>
            <p>Your membership stays active through the end of the billing cycle you already paid for, so you keep access to any remaining credits until that date. No prorated refunds are issued for mid-cycle cancellations, but you'll never be charged for a future cycle after requesting cancellation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-q w-full flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 text-left hover:bg-neutral-50 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900">Can I upgrade or downgrade my plan?</span>
            <svg class="faq-icon w-4 h-4 text-neutral-400 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a hidden px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-neutral-600 border-t border-neutral-100 pt-4 space-y-3">
            <p>Absolutely. Reach out and we'll switch your plan at your next billing cycle. Upgrades can typically be applied immediately mid-cycle if you want to start using the higher-tier credits right away — just let us know and we'll prorate or adjust accordingly.</p>
            <p>Downgrades take effect at the next renewal date so you keep your current tier's credits for the remainder of the month.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-q w-full flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 text-left hover:bg-neutral-50 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900">Can I stack my member discount with community discounts (veterans, teachers, etc.)?</span>
            <svg class="faq-icon w-4 h-4 text-neutral-400 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a hidden px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-neutral-600 border-t border-neutral-100 pt-4 space-y-2">
            <p>The member discount and community discounts (First Responder 15%, Teacher/Senior/Student 10%) <strong class="text-neutral-800">cannot be stacked</strong> on the same additional service — whichever discount is greater applies.</p>
            <p>Your monthly credits are already priced significantly below retail, so they don't interact with community discounts.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-q w-full flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 text-left hover:bg-neutral-50 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900">Does the member discount apply to seasonal packages and advanced treatments?</span>
            <svg class="faq-icon w-4 h-4 text-neutral-400 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a hidden px-6 pb-5 text-sm text-neutral-600 border-t border-neutral-100 pt-4 space-y-2">
            <p>Yes — your member discount applies to any additional service booked beyond your included credits, including seasonal packages, Vampire Facial (PRP), Scalp Therapy, Hairline Restoration, and Spray Tan.</p>
            <p>The discount only applies to the <em>additional</em> services — not the ones already covered by your credits.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-neutral-900">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-white mb-4">Ready to Commit to Your Glow?</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 mb-8">Join dozens of clients who've made Bliss Dermacare their monthly self-care ritual. Your skin will thank you.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <button
          data-plan="radiance-plan"
          data-plan-name="The Radiance Plan"
          data-plan-price="159"
          onclick="openMembershipSignup(this)"
          class="bg-primary-600 text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-all font-semibold text-sm shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
          Start Your Membership
        </button>
        <a href="/book/" class="text-sm text-neutral-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Or book a single appointment →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Membership Sign-Up Modal -->
  <div id="membership-modal" class="fixed inset-0 z-[200] hidden items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div id="membership-modal-overlay" class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-sm" onclick="closeMembershipModal()"></div>
    <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full max-w-lg z-10 overflow-y-auto max-h-[90vh]">
      <div class="p-6 border-b border-neutral-100">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary-500 mb-1">Join Bliss Dermacare</p>
            <h3 id="modal-plan-title" class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900">The Radiance Plan</h3>
            <p id="modal-plan-price" class="text-primary-600 font-semibold text-sm mt-0.5">$159/month · billed monthly · cancel anytime</p>
          </div>
          <button onclick="closeMembershipModal()" class="shrink-0 p-1.5 text-neutral-400 hover:text-neutral-700 hover:bg-neutral-100 rounded-lg transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <form id="membership-form" class="p-6 space-y-4" novalidate>
        <input type="hidden" id="modal-plan-input" name="plan" value="" />
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div>
            <label for="mem-name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700 mb-1.5">Full Name *</label>
            <input type="text" id="mem-name" name="name" required placeholder="Jane Smith"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-200 outline-none transition-all text-sm" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="mem-phone" class="block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700 mb-1.5">Phone Number *</label>
            <input type="tel" id="mem-phone" name="phone" required placeholder="(609) 366-0857"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-200 outline-none transition-all text-sm" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="mem-email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700 mb-1.5">Email Address *</label>
          <input type="email" id="mem-email" name="email" required placeholder="jane@example.com"
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-200 outline-none transition-all text-sm" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="mem-notes" class="block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700 mb-1.5">Skin goals or questions <span class="font-normal text-neutral-400">(optional)</span></label>
          <textarea id="mem-notes" name="notes" rows="3" placeholder="Any skin concerns, allergies, or goals you'd like us to know about..."
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-200 outline-none transition-all text-sm resize-none"></textarea>
        </div>

        <!-- Error -->
        <div id="mem-error" class="hidden items-start gap-3 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 text-red-800 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-sm">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          <span id="mem-error-text"></span>
        </div>

        <button id="mem-submit" type="submit"
          class="w-full bg-primary-600 text-white py-3.5 px-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-primary-700 disabled:opacity-60 disabled:cursor-not-allowed transition-all font-semibold text-sm shadow-sm hover:shadow-md flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          <svg id="mem-spinner" class="hidden animate-spin w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <circle class="opacity-25" cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4"/>
            <path class="opacity-75" fill="currentColor" d="M4 12a8 8 0 018-8v8z"/>
          </svg>
          <span id="mem-submit-label">Continue to Secure Checkout</span>
        </button>

        <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 text-center flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/></svg>
          Secure checkout via Stripe · Cancel anytime · No hidden fees
        </p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    // FAQ accordion
    document.querySelectorAll('.faq-q').forEach(btn => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const item = btn.closest('.faq-item')!;
        const ans  = item.querySelector('.faq-a') as HTMLElement;
        const icon = btn.querySelector('.faq-icon') as SVGElement;
        const open = !ans.classList.contains('hidden');
        ans.classList.toggle('hidden', open);
        icon.style.transform = open ? '' : 'rotate(180deg)';
      });
    });

    // Modal
    function openMembershipSignup(el: HTMLElement | {dataset: {plan:string, planName:string, planPrice:string}}) {
      const { plan, planName, planPrice } = (el as HTMLElement).dataset || el;
      const modal = document.getElementById('membership-modal')!;
      (document.getElementById('modal-plan-title') as HTMLElement).textContent = planName ?? '';
      (document.getElementById('modal-plan-price') as HTMLElement).textContent = `$${planPrice}/month · billed monthly · cancel anytime`;
      (document.getElementById('modal-plan-input') as HTMLInputElement).value = plan ?? '';
      modal.classList.remove('hidden');
      modal.classList.add('flex');
      document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
    }

    function closeMembershipModal() {
      const modal = document.getElementById('membership-modal')!;
      modal.classList.add('hidden');
      modal.classList.remove('flex');
      document.body.style.overflow = '';
    }

    // Make functions global
    (window as any).openMembershipSignup = openMembershipSignup;
    (window as any).closeMembershipModal = closeMembershipModal;

    // Form submission
    document.getElementById('membership-form')!.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();
      const name    = (document.getElementById('mem-name') as HTMLInputElement).value.trim();
      const phone   = (document.getElementById('mem-phone') as HTMLInputElement).value.trim();
      const email   = (document.getElementById('mem-email') as HTMLInputElement).value.trim();
      const notes   = (document.getElementById('mem-notes') as HTMLTextAreaElement).value.trim();
      const plan    = (document.getElementById('modal-plan-input') as HTMLInputElement).value;
      const errDiv  = document.getElementById('mem-error')!;
      const errText = document.getElementById('mem-error-text')!;
      const spinner = document.getElementById('mem-spinner')!;
      const label   = document.getElementById('mem-submit-label')!;
      const btn     = document.getElementById('mem-submit') as HTMLButtonElement;

      // Clear error
      errDiv.classList.add('hidden');
      errDiv.classList.remove('flex');

      // Validate
      if (!name) { showMemError('Please enter your full name.'); return; }
      if (!phone) { showMemError('Please enter your phone number.'); return; }
      if (!email || !/^[^\s@]+@[^\s@]+\.[^\s@]+$/.test(email)) { showMemError('Please enter a valid email address.'); return; }

      // Loading state
      btn.disabled = true;
      spinner.classList.remove('hidden');
      label.textContent = 'Processing…';

      try {
        const resp = await fetch('/.netlify/functions/create-membership-session', {
          method: 'POST',
          headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
          body: JSON.stringify({ plan, customerName: name, customerPhone: phone, customerEmail: email, notes }),
        });
        const data = await resp.json();
        if (!resp.ok || data.error) {
          showMemError(data.error || 'Something went wrong. Please try again or call us at (609) 366-0857.');
          btn.disabled = false;
          spinner.classList.add('hidden');
          label.textContent = 'Continue to Secure Checkout';
          return;
        }
        window.location.href = data.url;
      } catch {
        showMemError('Network error. Please check your connection and try again.');
        btn.disabled = false;
        spinner.classList.add('hidden');
        label.textContent = 'Continue to Secure Checkout';
      }

      function showMemError(msg: string) {
        errText.textContent = msg;
        errDiv.classList.remove('hidden');
        errDiv.classList.add('flex');
      }
    });
  </script>

</Layout>
